Interface Preorder<E>

All Superinterfaces:
Category<E,Boolean>
public interface Preorder<E> extends Category<E,Boolean>
Represents a Preorder as a Category.

Objects are elements of the preorder. There is at most one morphism between any two objects (a -> b iff a invalid input: '<'= b).

Since:
1.0
Author:
Silvere Martin-Michiellot, Gemini AI (Google DeepMind)
